org.eclipse.viatra.addon.databinding.runtime.collection

Interface ObservablePatternMatchCollection<M extends org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.IPatternMatch>


  • public interface ObservablePatternMatchCollection<M extends org.eclipse.viatra.query.runtime.api.IPatternMatch>
    Internal interface for building observable pattern match collections. The interface is implemented internally by both ObservablePatternMatchList and ObservablePatternMatchSet so the ObservablePatternMatchCollectionBuilder can work with both lists and sets.
